{"tid":2108602,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做過傳媒，講吓點解咁多大陸譯音","createTime":"2020-07-14T16:01:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T16:13:24.000Z","uid":288659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8dcc3ff996d1cdb5ac4c462456cc1aeb350a282e","tid":2108602,"uid":288659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:01:50.000Z","msg":"戴定頭盔，我係解釋緊個情況，唔係話咁樣係啱<br />\n<br />\n首先譯人名地名，唔係自己想點譯就點譯，<br />\n亦都無得話「以前」點點點<br />\n你自己嘅以前係噉，人哋嘅以前未必係噉<br />\n呢啲個人經驗之談根本拗唔完<br />\n<br />\n傳媒需要一個有認受性，或者係權威嘅譯名<br />\n球員譯名，最有權威嘅係馬會，所以跟馬會，一係就跟大眾<br />\n演員，可能係電影發行商，或者約定俗成<br />\n<br />\n其他人名，就無咁講究。<br />\n所以譯嗰陣會用一啲所謂人名字典<br />\n咁你畀人challenge嗰陣，都起碼可以話係跟字典<br />\n<br />\n同埋，人名唔係淨係得英文<br />\n有時有法文，德文，俄文，印度文，鬼識咩<br />\n所以呢啲人名字典都幾常用。<br />\n<br />\n但係，呢啲字典通常係大陸出，用普通話譯，所以就係你哋講嘅「跟大陸譯法」問題。<br />\n<br />\n地名同理。<br />\n<br />\n如果想用粵語譯法，就要有人搞一本粵語人名字典。"},{"pid":"b4a3f3764f4f179950e847876705e424e37c241f","tid":2108602,"uid":45934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:04:51.000Z","msg":"有trending 嘅新名要譯會點同行家夾<br />\n<br />\n比如trump 咁"},{"pid":"9bc6509e35be06ca0c29b98059d3e45004dc2000","tid":2108602,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:05:37.000Z","msg":"總之 Mason Greenwood 一定係要 碌木<br />\n唔係咩 格硬唔得"},{"pid":"6b09b8c2df67f5dd974eb496dd0dcd7d4d78d17b","tid":2108602,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b4a3f3764f4f179950e847876705e424e37c241f","tid":2108602,"uid":45934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:04:51.000Z","msg":"有trending 嘅新名要譯會點同行家夾<br />\n<br />\n比如trump 咁"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:06:58.000Z","msg":"點解trump 唔可以叫侵<br />\n叫川普特朗普<br />\n點讀都讀唔到侵個音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f2d3f132244169387cf96eb7ca37bcfc91de7ca","tid":2108602,"uid":79957,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:09:00.000Z","msg":"乜撚都冇解釋過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當你講嘅國語人名字典存在<br />\n都要講下存在左幾耐？既然如你所講，一直冇粵文版，咁以前嘅譯名標準係？而家要轉跟國語字典嘅原因又係？<br />\n<br />\n乜撚都冇講到，就撻朵話自己做傳媒，邏輯又唔通，香港media不被當作「專業」係有原因"},{"pid":"4881f978b1b3ff01aba83259bf34b31bf2f9f6fa","tid":2108602,"uid":288659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4a3f3764f4f179950e847876705e424e37c241f","tid":2108602,"uid":45934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:04:51.000Z","msg":"有trending 嘅新名要譯會點同行家夾<br />\n<br />\n比如trump 咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:09:16.000Z","msg":"未必會夾，eg 希拉里，希拉莉<br />\n仲有布什，布殊"},{"pid":"b856dfadc44e1dc9bd3cd8e30ae53b2042140cf3","tid":2108602,"uid":342115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bc6509e35be06ca0c29b98059d3e45004dc2000","tid":2108602,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:05:37.000Z","msg":"總之 Mason Greenwood 一定係要 碌木<br />\n唔係咩 格硬唔得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:09:20.000Z","msg":"有啲係連本身個英文都唔係咁讀然後唔知邊個懶醒有邊讀邊 <br />\nNeville 你好意思譯做<strong>尼維利</strong>？"},{"pid":"a21d5d82ed746b76bc77e2717bc29f8f425cefd6","tid":2108602,"uid":342115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b09b8c2df67f5dd974eb496dd0dcd7d4d78d17b","tid":2108602,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b4a3f3764f4f179950e847876705e424e37c241f","tid":2108602,"uid":45934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:04:51.000Z","msg":"有trending 嘅新名要譯會點同行家夾<br />\n<br />\n比如trump 咁"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:06:58.000Z","msg":"點解trump 唔可以叫侵<br />\n叫川普特朗普<br />\n點讀都讀唔到侵個音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:09:44.000Z","msg":"R 音點譯"},{"pid":"c7417c19c44d6004708b3439e0ea27c36dd76dcf","tid":2108602,"uid":689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b09b8c2df67f5dd974eb496dd0dcd7d4d78d17b","tid":2108602,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b4a3f3764f4f179950e847876705e424e37c241f",